com.interpss.simu.multicase.modify

Interface BusLoadChange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusLoadChangeImpl

    public interface BusLoadChange
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Load Change'. Class for defining bus load modification

    The following features are supported:

    • Change Type
    • Change Value
    • Code Change
    See Also:
    MCaseModifyPackage.getBusLoadChange()
